  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to initiate chat  with public chat participants\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n*Summary*: user should be able to open profile public chat member by clicking on his profile picture and go back.\r\n\r\n#### How it is implemented in mobile\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nWhen user clicks on user pic of any public chat participant, he is redirectied to:\r\n![lit](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/42754333-c81987d6-88fc-11e8-8fd5-b6713a5bac56.png)\r\nThe arrow in left top corner is redirecting user back to public chat.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n[comment]: # (Please summarise the solution and provide a task list on what needs to be fixed.)\r\n*Summary*: \r\n\r\n- [ ] add redirect to user profile from public chat\r\n- [ ] add way for user to get back to public chat\r\n",
